OL,3,CResident doctors in England to strike
OL,4,Cfor six days after Easter
OL,6,FResident doctors in England are to
OL,7,Fstrike for six days in an ongoing row
OL,8,Fover jobs and pay, the British Medical
OL,9,FAssociation (BMA) has announced.
OL,11,FThe latest round of industrial action
OL,12,Fwill start just after the Easter long
OL,13,Fweekend, from 7am on April 7 until
OL,14,F6.59am on April 13, the union has
OL,15,Fconfirmed.
OL,17,FThe doctors' union urged the
OL,18,FGovernment to "act fast" to prevent
OL,19,Fthe strikes from happening.
OL,26,@zD@OOUzD@XO]
