PN,31702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1774508671
OL,3,CResident doctors in England to strike
OL,4,Cfor six days after Easter
OL,6,FIt comes after the doctors' and
OL,7,Fdentists' pay review body the DDRB
OL,8,Frecommended a 3.5% uplift for doctors.
OL,10,FBMA Resident Doctors Committee
OL,11,Fchairman Jack Fletcher said: "We have
OL,12,Fbeen negotiating in good faith for
OL,13,Fweeks to try and end the simultaneous
OL,14,Fpay and jobs crises for resident
OL,15,Fdoctors.
OL,17,F"Frustratingly we had been making good
OL,18,Fprogress right up until the point, in
OL,19,Fthe last two weeks, when the
OL,20,FGovernment began to shift the
OL,21,Fgoalposts.
OL,26,@sD@^OUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1774508671
OL,3,CResident doctors in England to strike
OL,4,Cfor six days after Easter
OL,6,F"As talks progressed it became clear
OL,7,Fthat the money proposed for pay
OL,8,Fincreases was now going to be spread
OL,9,Fover three years.
OL,11,F"This is combined with today's pay
OL,12,Freview body (DDRB) recommendation of a
OL,13,F3.5% uplift pointing to yet more years
OL,14,Fin which our pay, at best, barely
OL,15,Ftreads water.
OL,17,F"We have made abundantly clear
OL,18,Fthroughout this dispute that our aim
OL,19,Fis pay restoration, and any deal that
OL,20,Fdid not move us substantially in that
OL,21,Fdirection was not going to fly."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUyD@AOU}D@`O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1774508671
OL,3,CResident doctors in England to strike
OL,4,Cfor six days after Easter
OL,6,FHe continues: "We also cannot ignore
OL,7,Fthat, thanks to global events,
OL,8,Feconomic indicators now point to years
OL,9,Fof greatly increased inflation.
OL,11,F"We are simply not going to put an
OL,12,Foffer to doctors that risks locking in
OL,13,Ffurther erosion of pay at a time when
OL,14,Fdoctors continue to leave the UK for
OL,15,Fother countries.
OL,17,F"We are not closing the door on talks.
OL,26,@nD@OOUsD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1774508671
OL,3,CResident doctors in England to strike
OL,4,Cfor six days after Easter
OL,6,F"We remain willing to negotiate and
OL,7,Fare eager to get a deal done if we can
OL,8,Fsimply recapture the early positive
OL,9,Fspirit of negotiations.
OL,11,F"No strikes need to happen, but
OL,12,FGovernment will need to act fast to
OL,13,Fprevent them."
